name: Cane & Upholstered Dining Chair - Natural
description: The Cane Rattan and Upholstered Dining Chair Natural, marries together the softness of our textiles with the impactful silhouette of the iconic chair design. The chair features a solid teak frame, a handwoven natural cane rattan backrest. For additional comfort the upholstered seat has been constructed using the highest quality foam padding. Customise your seat with your preferred fabric.
